// ============================================================
// FILE: aegis_proof_3_1_3_2_M1_prerequisites.psc.txt
// MODULE 1 OF 5 — Mathematical Prerequisites & Assumptions
// SOURCE: "AEGIS-PROOF-3.1 & 3.2: Mathematical Verification Suite
// Filter-Flash Monotonicity and Hybrid Mode Convergence"
// AUTHOR: Nnamdi Michael Okpala
// ORG: OBINexus Computing — AEGIS Project Team
// DATE: August 2025
