// MODULE 2 OF 5 — Real-Time Matrix Solver & Filter-Flash Medical
// SOURCE: "AEGIS-PROOF-4.1: Computational Implementation Specification
// Safety-Critical Hospital Systems with Fragile Tissue Interaction"
