// ============================================================
// FILE: diram_boolean_M1_truth_table.psc.txt
// MODULE 1 OF 5 — DIRAM Boolean Logic Truth Table
// Input Definitions & Gate Specification
// SOURCE: "DIRAM Boolean Logic Truth Table - Memory Management Gates"
