 CERTIFICATE_PINNING: REQUIRED

 STAGE 4: Cloud_Processing
 INPUT: encrypted_bundle over TLS 1.3
 ACTION: decrypt WITH session_key (server-side, authorized context only)
 ACTION: process -> generate Flash Events
 ACTION: sign result WITH ECDSA

 STAGE 5: Flash_Events
 SIGNED: ECDSA-P256
 STORED: in SecureFlashFilterDAG (see Module 3)
